---
const platform = "github"
const username = "withastro"
---
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-content">
    <div>
      <div class="rss-subscribe">
        <h3>Follow the updates on this site</h3>
        <div>
          <p>
            <a href="/rss.xml">RSS Link</a>
          </p>
          <p>Yes, RSS still exists \o/ Full text is provided in RSS so you'll never need to visit this site if you don't
            want to.</p>
          <p>Please notify if you have issues with the feed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-read-more">
      <h3>Read more</h3>
      <p>
        <a href="/author">Who am I?</a>
      </p>
      <p>I write about <a href="http://localhost:3000/tags/dev">software development</a>, <a
        href="http://localhost:3000/tags/hci">human-computer intearaction</a> and <a
        href="http://localhost:3000/tags/research">research</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        This is my corner of the web. I use it to practice writing. Writing also helps me to think (or forces me to).
        Which means I write to become better.
      </p>
      <p>
        I don't like using LinkedIn or such for content. I try to avoid social media as much as I can. Interacting would
        be easier there, but you can try Mastodon or LinkedIn to contact me. I'd like it.
      </p>
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p>
        You can find me on <a href="https://scholar.social/@arttuv">Mastodon</a> or <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/arttu-viljakainen/">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="copyright">
    <p>
      Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Arttu Viljakainen.
      All texts published are under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons
      Attribution-ShareAlike License</a> - attribution is required. Ask permission before using any of the photos on
      this site.
    </p>
    <p>
      Built with
      {` `}
      <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, hosted on <a href="https://pages.github.com/">GitHub Pages</a>. Icons by
      <a href="https://webkul.github.io/vivid/">Vivid</a> and <a href="https://www.iconfinder.com/Flatart">Flatart</a>
      and <a href="https://icons8.com">Icons8</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
    footer {
        border-top: 1px solid lightgray;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-content {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        flex-direction: row;
        font-weight: 200;
    }

    footer .copyright p {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: small;
    }

    .rss-subscribe {
        max-width: 45vw;
    }

    .footer-read-more {
        width: 45vw;
        max-width: 45vw;
    }

    .footer-read-more p {
        font-size: normal;
    }

    .footer-content h3 {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-weight: 200;
    }

    .rss-subscribe p {
        font-size: normal;
    }


    @media (max-width: 800px) {
        .footer-content {
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .rss-subscribe {
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .footer-read-more {
            max-width: 100%;
            width: 100%;
        }
    }

</style>